title: Dickies FR insulated duck jacket with hood
description: RJ701: The Flame-Resistant Insulated Duck Jacket with Hood, by Dickies.  This tough jacket is ergonomically designed to provide superior performance, protection and comfort.  It’s engineered with a durable 10.5 oz 100% cotton Duck fabric that’s FR treated, has an ARC Rating of 39, is rated HRC (Hazard Risk Category) Category Level 3 and is NFPA 70E compliant.  It will stand up to harsh working situations with double-needle stitched seams, two durable front pockets and rib knit cuffs and waistband.  While safe, it’s also built for comfort and utility with a durable zip front with interior storm flap, a three-piece adjustable drawstring hood, and a 10.5 oz Ultra Soft moda-quilt lining.  This rugged jacket will be with you for many long years.  Dickies, quality workwear since 1922.
